starting today?

389
00:16:10,230 --> 00:16:11,270
That's right!

390
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,900
Since this city's going to become
the new capital,

391
00:16:12,900 --> 00:16:14,910
there're a lot of people moving in.

392
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:16,870
It's no wonder we're getting
so many new kids.

393
00:16:16,870 --> 00:16:19,680
