It's sad, isn't it?

410
00:17:23,700 --> 00:17:25,510
Look who's talking.

411
00:17:25,510 --> 00:17:27,940
Are you saying that I'm
easily manipulated?

412
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:30,380
I'm merely reporting the facts.

413
00:17:30,380 --> 00:17:31,510
How so?

414
00:17:31,510 --> 00:17:31,880
