I see, this is another possibility.

439
00:18:52,230 --> 00:18:54,130
Another possible world.

440
00:18:54,330 --> 00:18:56,800
This current Self is the same way,
it's not my true Self.

441
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:58,730
I can be any way I wish to be.

442
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:03,870
