an Eva pilot as well!

443
00:19:05,610 --> 00:19:09,610
If you consider that, perhaps
this world isn't so bad.

444
00:19:09,610 --> 00:19:12,350
Still, even though the reality
itself might not be bad,

445
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:13,840
I could still hate myself.

446
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:17,120
It's your mind which takes
reality and separates it

447
00:19:17,120 --> 00:19:18,550
into what's bad and hateful.

448
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:21,960
It is only the mind which separates
reality from truth.

449
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:24,860
Your view of reality changes your
perception of its nature.

450
00:19:24,860 --> 00:19:28,500
It is all, literally, a matter
of perspective.

451
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:31,100
