that is your truth.

453
00:19:33,930 --> 00:19:35,840
That's the one that's formed

454
00:19:35,840 --> 00:19:38,740
by whatever narrow point of view
you choose to view it from.

455
00:19:38,740 --> 00:19:40,410
It's a perception that protects
you from the twisted truth.

456
00:19:40,410 --> 00:19:44,140
That's true, and one can have a
perspective that is far too small.

457
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:49,120
But a person can only see things
from the perspective they choose.

458
00:19:49,120 --> 00:19:51,320
One must learn to judge all things
via the perceived truths

459
00:19:51,320 --> 00:19:53,120
that one receives from others.

460
00:19:53,690 --> 00:19:55,790
For example, sunny days
make you feel good.

461
00:19:55,790 --> 00:19:57,790
Rainy days make you feel gloomy.

462
00:19:57,790 --> 00:20:00,690
