what you will believe to be so.

463
00:20:01,230 --> 00:20:04,060
But you can have fun on a
rainy day as well.

464
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:08,970
Your truth can be changed simply
by the way you accept it.

465
00:20:08,970 --> 00:20:11,130
That's how fragile the truth
for a human is.

466
00:20:11,810 --> 00:20:14,740
A person's truth is so simple
that most ignore it

467
00:20:14,740 --> 00:20:18,280
to concentrate on what they
think are deeper truths.

468
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:22,620
You, for example, are simply unused
to what it is to be liked.

469
00:20:22,620 --> 00:20:24,020
You've never learned how

470
00:20:24,020 --> 00:20:26,990
to deal with the fear of how others
feel about you, so you avoid it.

471
00:20:27,550 --> 00:20:30,890
But don't others hate me?

472
00:20:30,890 --> 00:20:35,450
